---
import LayoutRedesign from '../layouts/LayoutRedesign.astro';
---

<LayoutRedesign
  title="AI Agents That Work Like Teammates"
  description="Deploy lightweight AI agents that reason over your playbooks, take action, and keep your operators in the loop."
>

  <main class="bg-zinc-900">
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 mb-4">
            ai agents
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">
            Simple, reliable agents that follow your SOPs
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            No enterprise buzzwords—just polished assistants that read your playbooks, make logical decisions,
            and close the loop with your team. We build agents that stay in-bounds, document every step, and
            plug into the tools you already love.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-12">Where our agents shine</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Daily dashboards</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Agents pull metrics from your CRM, spreadsheets, or warehouse software and deliver a quick status
              digest with action items.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Inbox triage</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Route customer emails, flag escalations, draft replies, and keep humans in the loop for final send.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Onboarding flows</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Collect docs, update internal databases, and notify teammates when it’s time for a personal touch.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Field reports</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Turn technician notes, voice memos, or photos into structured reports and push them back into your systems.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Compliance reminders</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Agents check checklists, document proof, and surface issues before audits notice them.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Knowledge search</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Private RAG pipelines answer team questions using your SOPs, manuals, and case studies—without exposing data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">Our agent toolkit</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li>
                <span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Reasoning models:</span>
                Llama 3.1, Claude, and GPT-4o-mini tuned for fast, logical decision making.
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Memory + context:</span>
                Vector stores, Redis caches, and temporal memory so agents learn without leaking data.
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Action layer:</span>
                n8n, Netlify Functions, custom APIs, and webhooks to complete real-world tasks.
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Guardrails:</span>
                Rubrics, sandbox testing, and human handoffs so nothing goes rogue.
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Observability:</span>
                Automatic transcripts, analytics, and rollback tools to keep leadership comfortable.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50">What launch looks like</h3>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li>Document the workflow and “definition of done”.</li>
              <li>Build a sandbox agent with synthetic data.</li>
              <li>Run pilot with a small user group and daily standups.</li>
              <li>Scale to production with monitoring and feedback loops.</li>
            </ol>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Most teams see their first agent in production within two weeks, with incremental releases after.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-10">Polished, casual experience for your team</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Friendly UI, serious results</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Chat-style interfaces with inline approvals keep things familiar. Agents explain each step so operators
              always know what happened.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Bring your team along</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Every rollout includes training sessions, resource guides, and built-in feedback capture so adoption sticks.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Cost that scales with wins</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              Fixed-monthly pricing to maintain agents, plus optional lane-based pricing if you want to grow the fleet.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Always under your control</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
              You decide when agents act autonomously, when they pause, and when humans review. It’s your process—we just automate it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">FAQs</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">How “hands-off” can agents be?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  You choose. Many clients start with suggestions + human approval, then graduate to automatic actions once the team trusts the flow.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Do we need our own data warehouse?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Not required. We integrate with spreadsheets, CRMs, Firestore, PostgreSQL, or whatever system you live in today.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">How do you keep things safe?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Every agent ships with audit logs, rate limits, and scope boundaries. If something looks off, operators can pause the agent instantly.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Can we bring our own models?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Yes. We support OpenAI, Anthropic, Vertex AI, and fully self-hosted models, depending on your compliance needs.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-3">Let’s build your agent playbook</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 mb-4">
              We’ll map workflows, highlight quick wins, and propose a rollout plan that keeps your operators smiling.
            </p>
            <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">Book a working session</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

</LayoutRedesign>
